{"tid":729050,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"lunch食車仔麵谷鬼氣","createTime":"2018-07-04T08:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T10:31:27.000Z","uid":119688,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e66f3838c89b701f29fe695da15e798b5e6c129b","tid":729050,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"見間鋪頭幾多人食<br />\n咪排隊試下囉 餓左成朝<br />\n<br />\n車仔麵來來去去都係果d價錢<br />\n心諗叫三樣餸頂盡咪四十幾<br />\n無睇幾錢拎住張五十蚊<br />\n點完餸收銀話多謝86蚊<br />\n哇你老母,當堂嚇到懶屎心都寒<br />\n個心勁想話唔要,又唔想咁婆媽<br />\n排隊前前後後又有幾條囡囡幾正<br />\n迫於無耐,要扮型比錢<br />\n無理由咁柒話唔要<br />\n唉 真係谷鬼氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5931da69d06b8724e0b4b45c6b007f70f5b7541","tid":729050,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccb73d0c6b8024cee51c1c170c0ccecf8c12b4b","tid":729050,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5931da69d06b8724e0b4b45c6b007f70f5b7541","tid":729050,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"係咪同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d9e028546689c1c2212150706724bb59f1107f","tid":729050,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccb73d0c6b8024cee51c1c170c0ccecf8c12b4b","tid":729050,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5931da69d06b8724e0b4b45c6b007f70f5b7541","tid":729050,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"係咪同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"